<plot>David is a high-strung young man with Tourette's Syndrome. Meg is a painfully shy young woman with Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder. Whether for a joke, or out of genuine goodwill, their mutual friend and Psychology student Lawrence decides to do a little matchmaking, and talks them into a game of golf together. The initial meeting does not go off quite well, but when a horrible accident occurs and Lawrence is killed Meg and David find themselves with no choice but to try their best to cover up the incident.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?220314</url></doc>
